    <p class="two">
        <br><br>
        It has been a pleasure serving you.
        We at Bake a Cake's pride in giving priority to their customers and looking after their needs.
        <br><br>
        Thank you again for choosing us. Looking forward to having you as one of our valued customers again.
    </p>
</div>

